name: Crystal for ROBLOX (2016 UI for Roblox)
description:
The first 2016 recreation for Roblox beating the others by a month. Also the most feature-packed. :) developed by iiboiis on roblox
Features included: - ROBLOX 2016 logo in header - White text - Chat & Party fixed - Blue chat bubbles with white text - Dark received bubbles - Removed age text - Removed Shop from header - Restored text to 'Play' button - Replace Roblox Premium logo with BC. - Old Colors Restored - Old Robux Icon - Colored BC icons - Notifications in red - Shadows on games page, home page and catalog!

user.name: John R.

additional_info:
Change Log

CHANGE LOG IS ONLY SAVED FROM 2.3.0 FORWARD. SCROLL TO VIEW THE LOGS (logs are dated in est) v2.3: old robux icon, bc moved and full size, add source sans - 9/21/19 v2.3.1: colored like button and meter. v2.3.2: added color to tabs (servers, store, and about) and to loading 12/29/19 v2.3.3: old roblox logo on play game loading - 1/1/20 (happy new year) v2.3.4: fix logo invisible from header - 2/27/20 v2.3.5: svgs are now all data urls. this was done because of the frequent wayback machine crashes - 3/28/20 v2.4: fixed major bugs and added color to many of the ui elements (THIS IS A MANDATORY UPDATE) - 4/1/20 (not a joke) v2.4.1: places notifications in the header - 4/21/20 v2.4.2: removes notifications due to bugs with the sidebar - 5/9/20 v3.0: restoring the error pages to look exactly how they used to and some other feature updates - 5/10/20 v3.0.1: bug fixes due to layout changes - 5/13/20 v3.1: move builders club icon back into place - 5/14/20 v3.1.1: fix chat bubble appearing in black on some pages - 5/15/20 v3.1.2: fix catalog items not showing up - 5/16/20 v4.0: biggest feature update yet! adds colors to places that didn't have it, adds classic games layout, adds classic catalog layout, adds notifications back, reduces radius and even more! - 5/19/20 v4.0.1: restores some old icons - 5/20/20 v4.1: another big feature update! classic background, top-bar hoverover box, blue "see all" button, blue links in description, blue VIP servers button, fixed chat message colors, fixed chat icons, changed catalog entirely to look more 2016-y and added more older icons - 5/26/20 v4.2 improvements to classic feel, old like-dislike-favorites layout, better play label, old top bar labels and more
